                            <h2>​Accessible content​</h2>

                            <p>​We use simple language and clear link text to help you navigate the census website. You can navigate most of the website using speech recognition software and listen using a screen reader. Our <a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/accessibility-statement">accessibility statement</a> gives more detail on how compatible this website is with assistive technology.​</p>

                            <p>​Information about the census is also available in the following accessible formats:​</p>

                            <ul>
                                <li><a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/help/languages-and-accessibility/accessibility/british-sign-language">videos with British Sign Language, subtitles and audio​</a></li>
