                                <li><a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/help/languages-and-accessibility/accessibility/easy-read">easy read guidance​</a></li>
                                <li><a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/help/languages-and-accessibility/accessibility/large-print">large-print information</a></li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2>If you need help</h2>

                            <p>To get help to complete your census you can also:​</p>

                            <ul>
                                <li>ask someone else to fill it in for you, or help you if you can’t do it yourself​</li>
                                <li><a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/help/find-a-support-centre">find a support centre</a>, where you can get help to complete your census online</li>
                                <li>access web chat, call us on the phone or use the text relay system from our <a href="{{pageInfo.rootPath}}/contact-us">contact us page</a>​</li>
                                <li>read translations of <a href="https://eqendtoend.netlify.app/end-to-end/languages-copy/">information about the census in different languages</a></li>
